<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (yạ knysẗ yạ sẖʿb ạlly fdạky dh ʿynyh shrạnh btrʿạky)2
 wạllyl ạ̹n ṭwl wyạky ạlfjr hysṭʿ llqạky
 1- (ạlywm ạ̉hh jạylk wạ̹n ṭạlt ạ̉tʿạbk byqwlk hạnt)2
 dạ msyḥk ʿmrh mạkạn ṣạmt wlạ ʿmrh fy ywm rạḥ ynsạky
 2- (yạ lʿạzr kẖd bạlk mnhạ dy rfqẗ wḥydẗ ṭmnhạ)2
 ʿn mjd ạsḥq qwm klmhạ ʿn ḥbh wqwl lhạ yạ hnạky
 3- (ạ̉bwạb ạlhạwyẗ ạlly qṣạdk lạ htqwy ʿly ạṣgẖr ạ̉wlạdk)2
 ạ̹blys msẖ ṭạyq ạ̉mjạdk mgẖlwb ạ̹n kạn ytḥdạky</lyrics>
